# Code — Site Principal (index.html)

**Fișier:** `index.html`  
**Tip:** HTML single-file (2400+ linii)  
**Deploy:** Cloudflare Worker la ruta `/`  
**Limbi:** EN / RO / FR / DE

## Descriere

Site-ul principal al agenției Pro Web Architects. Conține toate secțiunile:

| Secțiune | Descriere |
|----------|-----------|
| NAV | Fixed navbar cu language switcher + dark mode |
| TICKER | Bandă animată cu servicii |
| HERO | Headline mare + stats + CTA buttons |
| SERVICES | 6 carduri servicii cu template modals |
| PORTFOLIO | 8 proiecte cu SVG previews reale |
| METHODOLOGY | 4 faze de lucru |
| PRICING | 3 planuri (€500 / €2.500 / €8.000) |
| TESTIMONIALS | Slider cu 4 testimoniale |
| BLOG | 3 articole preview |
| FAQ | 5 întrebări accordion |
| CTA BANNER | Secțiune violet cu CTA |
| CONTACT | Formular complet → Airtable |
| FOOTER | Complet cu toate linkurile |

## Features

- 🌍 **Multilingv** — sistem i18n custom EN/RO/FR/DE
- 🌙 **Dark Mode** — toggle complet
- 📱 **Mobile Menu** — fullscreen cu animație
- 📊 **Scroll Progress Bar** — indicator progres
- 🎠 **Testimonial Slider** — responsive cu dots
- 🖼️ **Template Modals** — demo vizual interactiv pentru fiecare serviciu
- 📋 **Project Modals** — detalii proiect cu metrici și tech stack
- ✅ **Form Validation** — client-side cu error messages

## Cod Complet

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="light">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Pro Web Architects — Monolithic Precision</title>
<meta name="description" content="High-precision web engineering. Custom architectures that convert. No templates. No compromises."/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300..700&family=Roboto+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms"></script>
<script>
tailwind.config = {
  darkMode:"class",
  theme:{extend:{
    colors:{
      "primary":"#3700b2","primary-container":"#4e0fea","primary-fixed":"#e5deff",
      "on-primary":"#ffffff","on-primary-container":"#c4b9ff",
      "secondary":"#1960a3","secondary-container":"#7db6ff","on-secondary":"#ffffff",
      "surface":"#f9f9f9","surface-variant":"#e2e2e2","surface-container":"#eeeeee",
      "surface-container-high":"#e8e8e8","surface-container-low":"#f3f3f3",
      "surface-container-lowest":"#ffffff","on-surface":"#1b1b1b",
      "on-surface-variant":"#484456","outline":"#797488","outline-variant":"#c9c3d9",
      "tertiary":"#383838","tertiary-container":"#4f4f4f",
    },
    fontFamily:{"headline":["Inter","sans-serif"],"body":["Inter","sans-serif"],"label":["Space Grotesk","sans-serif"],"mono":["Roboto Mono","monospace"]},
    borderRadius:{DEFAULT:"0px",lg:"0px",xl:"0px",full:"9999px"},
  }}
}
</script>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --primary:#3700b2;--primary-light:#4e0fea;--primary-fixed:#e5deff;
  --secondary:#1960a3;--surface:#f9f9f9;--surface-low:#f3f3f3;
  --on-surface:#1b1b1b;--on-surface-variant:#484456;
  --outline-variant:#c9c3d9;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--surface);color:var(--on-surface);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden}

/* ── CURSOR ── */
/* custom cursor removed */

/* ── GRID BG ── */
.arch-grid{background-image:radial-gradient(circle,#c9c3d9 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;opacity:.2}

/* ── SHIMMER ── */
.shimmer{position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.shimmer::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:-50%;left:-60%;width:40%;height:200%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,.15),transparent);transform:skewX(-20deg);transition:left .6s ease}
.shimmer:hover::after{left:120%}

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes slideIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}}
@keyframes ticker{from{transform:translateX(0)}to{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
@keyframes pulse-dot{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.4}}
@keyframes scanline{0%{top:0}100%{top:100%}}

.fade-up{animation:fadeUp .8s ease both}
.fade-up-2{animation:fadeUp .8s .15s ease both}
.fade-up-3{animation:fadeUp .8s .3s ease both}
.fade-up-4{animation:fadeUp .8s .45s ease both}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav.main-nav{position:fixed;top:0;width:100%;z-index:100;background:rgba(249,249,249,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant)}
.dark nav.main-nav{background:rgba(10,10,10,.92)}

/* ── TICKER ── */
.ticker-wrap{overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;border-top:1px solid var(--outline-variant);border-bottom:1px solid var(--outline-variant)}
.ticker-inner{display:inline-flex;animation:ticker 30s linear infinite}
.ticker-inner:hover{animation-play-state:paused}

/* ── SECTION LABEL ── */
.sec-label{font-family:'Roboto Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--primary)}

/* ── CARDS ── */
.project-card{border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);transition:all .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}
.project-card:hover{background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border-color:var(--primary)}
.project-card:hover .card-num{color:rgba(255,255,255,.15)}
.project-card:hover .card-tag{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)}
.project-card:hover .card-arrow{color:#fff}

/* ── SERVICE CARDS ── */
.service-card{border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);transition:all .35s ease;cursor:pointer}
.service-card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(55,0,178,.12);border-color:var(--primary)}
.service-card:hover .service-icon{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}

/* ── PRICE CARDS ── */
.price-card{border:1px solid var(--outline-variant);transition:all .3s ease}
.price-card.featured{background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border-color:var(--primary)}
.price-card.featured .price-feature{color:rgba(255,255,255,.8)}
.price-card:not(.featured):hover{border-color:var(--primary);transform:translateY(-4px)}

/* ── LANG SWITCHER ── */
.lang-btn{font-family:'Roboto Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid transparent;transition:all .2s}
.lang-btn.active,.lang-btn:hover{border-color:var(--primary);color:var(--primary)}

/* ── ACCORDION ── */
.faq-content{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .4s ease}
.faq-content.open{max-height:300px}
.faq-toggle{transition:transform .3s ease}
.faq-item.open .faq-toggle{transform:rotate(45deg)}

/* ── MOBILE MENU ── */
.mobile-menu{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--surface);z-index:99;transform:translateX(100%);transition:transform .4s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}
.mobile-menu.open{transform:translateX(0)}

/* ── TEMPLATE MODAL ── */
.template-modal{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(10,10,10,.9);z-index:200;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.template-modal.show{display:flex}

/* ── TESTIMONIAL ── */
.testimonial-track{display:flex;transition:transform .5s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}

/* ── SCROLL PROGRESS ── */
.scroll-progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:2px;background:var(--primary);z-index:200;transition:width .1s linear}

/* ── DARK MODE ── */
.dark body{background:#0a0a0a;color:#f1f1f1}
.dark .arch-grid{background-image:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(255,255,255,.08) 1px,transparent 1px)}
.dark .project-card{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08);background:#111}
.dark .project-card:hover{background:var(--primary)}
.dark .service-card{background:#111;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.dark .price-card:not(.featured){background:#111;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.dark .faq-item{border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.dark input,.dark textarea,.dark select{background:#1a1a1a;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:#f1f1f1}

/* ── UTILS ── */
.text-gradient{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-light));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.border-primary-soft{border-color:rgba(55,0,178,.2)}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Scroll Progress -->
<div class="scroll-progress" id="scrollProgress"></div>

