      </h1>

      <p class="fade-up-3 text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-12 leading-relaxed" data-key="hero_sub">
        High-precision web engineering for modern brands. We don't build websites — we design monolithic systems that endure and convert.
      </p>

      <!-- Stats row -->
