    faq1_q:"How long does a project take?", faq1_a:"A landing page takes 2–3 weeks. A full e-commerce site takes 4–8 weeks. We provide realistic timelines and stick to them.",
    faq2_q:"Why not use WordPress or Shopify?", faq2_a:"Templates limit you. Custom code means superior performance, better security, unique design, and unlimited scalability.",
    faq3_q:"What happens after launch?", faq3_a:"Full training on your CMS, 30–180 days post-launch support depending on plan, and optional monthly maintenance.",
    faq4_q:"Do you work with international clients?", faq4_a:"Yes. We work across Europe and beyond. Communication in English, Romanian, French, and German.",
    faq5_q:"How do payments work?", faq5_a:"50% upfront, 50% on delivery. Milestone-based payments available for larger projects.",
    cta_title:"Ready to Build?", cta_sub:"Join brands that prioritize precision over trends. Let's architect your digital legacy.",
